sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sysauto_script"><sysauto_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><business_calendar/><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><entered_time/><name>GR CSM Case autoclose</name><offset/><offset_type>0</offset_type><run_as display_value="System Administrator">6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441</run_as><run_as_tz/><run_dayofmonth>1</run_dayofmonth><run_dayofweek>1</run_dayofweek><run_period/><run_start>2021-09-30 14:37:21</run_start><run_time>1970-01-01 09:00:00</run_time><run_type>daily</run_type><script><![CDATA[// This script automatically closes GR CSM Case tickets that are resolved
// and haven't been updated in the specified number of days.
// To place a comment in the GR CSM Case, uncomment the "gr.comments" line.

autoCloseGRCase();

function autoCloseGRCase() {
    //var ps = gs.getProperty('glide.ui.autoclose.time');
    //var pn = parseInt(ps);
    var pn = 1; // Auto-close after 1 day (24 hours)
    var queryTime = new GlideDateTime();
    queryTime.addDaysUTC(-pn);

    if (pn > 0) {
        var gr = new GlideRecord('x_gur_grt_csm_case');
        gr.addQuery('state', '6'); // Resolved
        gr.addQuery('sys_updated_on', '<', queryTime);
        gr.query();
		
        gs.info(gr.getRowCount() + ' resolved records found');
        while (gr.next()) {
            gr.state = 3; // Closed
            //  gr.comments = 'GR CSM Case automatically closed after ' + pn + ' days in the Resolved state.';
            gr.active = false;
            gr.closed_by = gr.resolved_by;
            gr.update();
        }
    }
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>Nick.Nobis@rate.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-09-30 14:39:29</sys_created_on><sys_id>d8f0d42b1b7abc901242a7562a4bcbd9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>GR CSM Case autoclose</sys_name><sys_package display_value="GR CSM Template" source="x_gur_grt_csm">7f5f0b37c9cd945fce0f66d4abe63411</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="GR CSM Template">7f5f0b37c9cd945fce0f66d4abe63411</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_d8f0d42b1b7abc901242a7562a4bcbd9</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Nick.Nobis@rate.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-09-30 14:39:29</sys_updated_on><time_zone/><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_gur_grt_csm_case</collection><condition>current.state == '3'  || current.state == '7' || current.state == '8'</condition><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="x_gur_grt_csm_case">active=true^assignment_groupISEMPTY^ORassignment_group=4f47ee491b2460101242a7562a4bcbd9^EQ<item endquery="false" field="active" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="true"/><item endquery="false" field="assignment_group" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="ISEMPTY" or="false" value=""/><item display_table="sys_user_group" display_value="Servicing" endquery="false" field="assignment_group" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="true" value="4f47ee491b2460101242a7562a4bcbd9"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>mark_resolved</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[setResolutionFields();

function setResolutionFields() {
    if (current.resolved_by.nil())
        current.resolved_by = gs.getUserID();

    if (current.resolved_at.nil()) {
        var gdt = new GlideDateTime();
        current.resolved_at = gdt.getDisplayValue();
    }

    // Update the fields that indicate the time and duration of this incident from open to resolve.
    // Keep track of duration as a glide_duration value (dd hh:mm:ss) and as a pure number of seconds.
    // Both calendar time and business time are maintained.

    var dataChange = current.opened_at.changes() || current.resolved_at.changes();
    var opened = current.opened_at.getDisplayValue();
    var resolved = current.resolved_at.getDisplayValue();

    if (dataChange || current.business_duration.nil())
		current.business_duration = GlideDateTime.subtract(current.opened_at, current.resolved_at);
        //current.business_duration = gs.calDateDiff(opened, resolved, false);

    if (dataChange || current.calendar_duration.nil())
        current.calendar_duration = gs.dateDiff(opened, resolved, false);
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>Nick.Nobis@rate.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-09-29 10:07:13</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>25894a8b1bfaf8901242a7562a4bcb3b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>mark_resolved</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="GR CSM Template" source="x_gur_grt_csm">7f5f0b37c9cd945fce0f66d4abe63411</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="GR CSM Template">7f5f0b37c9cd945fce0f66d4abe63411</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_25894a8b1bfaf8901242a7562a4bcb3b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Nick.Nobis@rate.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-10-07 07:36:16</sys_updated_on><template>assignment_group=^EQ</template><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=25894a8b1bfaf8901242a7562a4bcb3b"/></record_update>
